			<h1>
				Does my family history put me at a higher risk for Alzheimer’s Disease than other people?
			</h1>
			<h2>
				Genetic testing is usually considered when a person might be at higher risk for a particular condition. Here we help you explore whether you may be at greater risk of getting late-onset Alzheimer&rsquo;s Disease, the form which affects older people, based on your family history.
